results.p: WinSCP is a free file manager for Windows supporting FTP, SFTP, S3 and WebDAV.

results.t: Official Site :: Free SFTP and FTP client for Windows
results.p: WinSCP is a popular SFTP client and FTP client for Microsoft Windows! Copy file between a local computer and remote servers using FTP, FTPS, SCP, SFTP, WebDAV ...
